    sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant Frontend as VeryDot Frontend
    participant Identity as Identity Pallet
    participant IPFS as IPFS Network
    participant Verifier as Industry Verifier
    participant Chain as Polkadot Chain
    
    Note over User, Chain: Identity Creation & Verification Flow
    
    User->>Frontend: Create profile with industry specialization
    Frontend->>User: Request documents & portfolio
    User->>Frontend: Upload verification documents
    
    Note over Frontend, IPFS: Document Storage Phase
    Frontend->>IPFS: Store documents (portfolio, certificates)
    IPFS->>Frontend: Return document hashes
    
    Note over Frontend, Chain: On-Chain Identity Creation
    Frontend->>Identity: set_extended_identity(base_info, industry_fields, doc_hashes)
    Identity->>Chain: Store identity data
    Chain->>Identity: Confirm storage
    Identity->>Frontend: Identity created (pending verification)
    Frontend->>User: Profile created - verification pending
    
    Note over User, Chain: Verification Request Process
    User->>Frontend: Request verification for specific industry
    Frontend->>Identity: request_verification(industry_type)
    Identity->>Identity: Update status to "verification_requested"
    Identity->>Frontend: Verification request registered
    
    Note over Verifier, Chain: Verifier Review Process
    Verifier->>Identity: Get pending verifications
    Identity->>Verifier: Return verification requests
    Verifier->>IPFS: Retrieve documents using hashes
    IPFS->>Verifier: Return document contents
    
    Note over Verifier: Manual Review Process
    Verifier->>Verifier: Review portfolio & credentials
    Verifier->>Identity: provide_judgement(verified/rejected, notes)
    Identity->>Chain: Update verification status
    Chain->>Identity: Confirm update
    
    Note over Identity, User: Notification & Completion
    Identity->>Frontend: Emit VerificationCompleted event
    Frontend->>User: Notify verification result
    
    Note over User, Chain: Multi-Industry Expansion (Optional)
    User->>Frontend: Add expertise in new industry
    Frontend->>Identity: add_industry_extension(new_industry, fields)
    Identity->>Chain: Update identity with new industry
    Chain->>Identity: Confirm update
    Identity->>Frontend: Industry added successfully
    Frontend->>User: New industry expertise added